            No Mercy             001         (2015) (Digital) (Son of Ultron-Empire)
            
            Past Aways           001         (2015) (Digital) (Son of Ultron-Empire)
            
            Rebels               001         (2015) (Digital) (Son of Ultron-Empire)
            
            RunLoveKill           01 (of 08) (2015) (Digital) (Son of Ultron-Empire)
            
            The Infinite Loop     01 (of 06) (2015) (Digital)               (Empire)

            Yet another very good month, with eight debuts making the cut. Image

            extend a warm welcome to Black Mask Studios for the remaining one!!
